            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EIntegrity%20is%20the%20missing%20ingredient%20in%20many%20leaders%20today.%20Nehemiah%2C%20however%2C%20taught%20and%20modeled%20a%20sacrificial%20lifestyle%20that%20was%20above%20reproach.%20Although%20he%20had%20a%20right%20to%20be%20pampered%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20place%20a%20heavy%20burden%20on%20the%20people%20(Nehemiah%205%3A15).%20Although%20others%20had%20lorded%20it%20over%20the%20people%2C%20Nehemiah%20devoted%20himself%20to%20the%20work%20on%20the%20wall%20(v.%2016).%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20never%20demanded%20the%20fine%20food%20allotted%20to%20him%20as%20governor%20(v.%2018).%20He%20was%20a%20man%20of%20rare%20integrity%20who%20led%20by%20his%20example.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20life%20of%20integrity%20demands%20a%20lifestyle%20of%20accountability%20that%20involves%20one's%20money%2C%20priorities%2C%20and%20motives.%20God%20was%20so%20blessed%20by%20Job's%20integrity%20that%20He%20described%20him%20as%20%22the%20finest%20man%20in%20all%20the%20earth-a%20man%20of%20complete%20integrity%22%20(Job%202%3A3).%20In%20the%20New%20Testament%2C%20Peter%20reminded%20the%20elders%20not%20to%20be%20greedy%20for%20money%2C%20but%20eager%20to%20serve%3B%20not%20to%20lord%20it%20over%20those%20entrusted%20to%20them%2C%20but%20to%20be%20examples%20to%20the%20flock%20(1%20Peter%205%3A2-3).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThose%20you%20lead%20can%20tell%20if%20your%20heart%20is%20influenced%20by%20the%20work%20or%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20work.%20If%20you%20aspire%20to%20leadership%2C%20seek%20integrity.%20God%20will%20be%20sure%20to%20make%20a%20place%20for%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
