            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Corinthians%208%3A1-13%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Corinthians%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EFood%20Sacrificed%20to%20Idols%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20regarding%20your%20question%20about%20food%20that%20has%20been%20offered%20to%20idols.%20Yes%2C%20we%20know%20that%20%26%23x201C%3Bwe%20all%20have%20knowledge%26%23x201D%3B%20about%20this%20issue.%20But%20while%20knowledge%20makes%20us%20feel%20important%2C%20it%20is%20love%20that%20strengthens%20the%20church.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAnyone%20who%20claims%20to%20know%20all%20the%20answers%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20really%20know%20very%20much.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20person%20who%20loves%20God%20is%20the%20one%20whom%20God%20recognizes.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Some%20manuscripts%20read%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20person%20who%20loves%20has%20full%20knowledge.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%2C%20what%20about%20eating%20meat%20that%20has%20been%20offered%20to%20idols%3F%20Well%2C%20we%20all%20know%20that%20an%20idol%20is%20not%20really%20a%20god%20and%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20may%20be%20so-called%20gods%20both%20in%20heaven%20and%20on%20earth%2C%20and%20some%20people%20actually%20worship%20many%20gods%20and%20many%20lords.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20for%20us%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3EThere%20is%20one%20God%2C%20the%20Father%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eby%20whom%20all%20things%20were%20created%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20for%20whom%20we%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EAnd%20there%20is%20one%20Lord%2C%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethrough%20whom%20all%20things%20were%20created%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20through%20whom%20we%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20believers%20know%20this.%20Some%20are%20accustomed%20to%20thinking%20of%20idols%20as%20being%20real%2C%20so%20when%20they%20eat%20food%20that%20has%20been%20offered%20to%20idols%2C%20they%20think%20of%20it%20as%20the%20worship%20of%20real%20gods%2C%20and%20their%20weak%20consciences%20are%20violated.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20true%20that%20we%20can%26%23x2019%3Bt%20win%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20approval%20by%20what%20we%20eat.%20We%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20lose%20anything%20if%20we%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20eat%20it%2C%20and%20we%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20gain%20anything%20if%20we%20do.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20must%20be%20careful%20so%20that%20your%20freedom%20does%20not%20cause%20others%20with%20a%20weaker%20conscience%20to%20stumble.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20if%20others%20see%20you%26%23x2014%3Bwith%20your%20%26%23x201C%3Bsuperior%20knowledge%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2014%3Beating%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20an%20idol%2C%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20they%20be%20encouraged%20to%20violate%20their%20conscience%20by%20eating%20food%20that%20has%20been%20offered%20to%20an%20idol%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20because%20of%20your%20superior%20knowledge%2C%20a%20weak%20believer%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Ebrother%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%208%3A13.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20whom%20Christ%20died%20will%20be%20destroyed.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20when%20you%20sin%20against%20other%20believers%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Ebrothers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20encouraging%20them%20to%20do%20something%20they%20believe%20is%20wrong%2C%20you%20are%20sinning%20against%20Christ.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20if%20what%20I%20eat%20causes%20another%20believer%20to%20sin%2C%20I%20will%20never%20eat%20meat%20again%20as%20long%20as%20I%20live%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20I%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20want%20to%20cause%20another%20believer%20to%20stumble.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E"
        },
