            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EPsalm%2033%3A1-11%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_1%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EPsalm%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20the%20godly%20sing%20for%20joy%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eit%20is%20fitting%20for%20the%20pure%20to%20praise%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_2%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EPraise%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20with%20melodies%20on%20the%20lyre%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Emake%20music%20for%20him%20on%20the%20ten-stringed%20harp.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_3%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESing%20a%20new%20song%20of%20praise%20to%20him%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eplay%20skillfully%20on%20the%20harp%2C%20and%20sing%20with%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_4%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20holds%20true%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20we%20can%20trust%20everything%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_5%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20loves%20whatever%20is%20just%20and%20good%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20unfailing%20love%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20fills%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_6%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20merely%20spoke%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20heavens%20were%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20breathed%20the%20word%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20all%20the%20stars%20were%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_7%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20assigned%20the%20sea%20its%20boundaries%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20locked%20the%20oceans%20in%20vast%20reservoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_8%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20the%20whole%20world%20fear%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20let%20everyone%20stand%20in%20awe%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_9%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20when%20he%20spoke%2C%20the%20world%20began!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EIt%20appeared%20at%20his%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_10%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20frustrates%20the%20plans%20of%20the%20nations%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20thwarts%20all%20their%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22psal_33_11%22%20bk%3D%22psal%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20plans%20stand%20firm%20forever%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehis%20intentions%20can%20never%20be%20shaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E"
